 InsertDummyData;D;NotFixedKeys;WrapBackticks;WrapColons;category;cid;col_spec;column;data;event;event_type;fixed_keys;keywords;lipsum;n;name;organisation;person;person_names;presentation;presentation_media;presentation_type;presenter;sql;stems;table;thing_names;tid;type;type_spec;videos;youtube_video
вНЭ Insert dummy data into the database for testing
вНЭ First tests considered:
вНЭ - /videos?search= should return all videos with matching terms
вНЭ - /videos?presenter=p_name should return all videos by presenter p_name
вНЭ - /videos?search=p_name       should include videos by presenter p_name
вНЭ FIXME this is not comprehensive. Fields essential to the video library are used, but many are not.

вНЭ Start by generating joined data and deconstructing it into the normalised database, then loop over each table and insert.

вНЭ CONFIG
 keywordsвЖРgenerator.keywords
 stemsвЖРgenerator.stemmable[;2]
 person_namesвЖР'Geoff' 'Streeter' 'John' 'Scholes' 'Iverson' 'Dolor' 'Fugiat' 'Orange' 'Rich' 'Park' 'Jada' 'Andrade' 'Andy' 'Karen' 'Fiona' 'Jason' 'Peter' 'Silas'
 thing_namesвЖР'APL' 'Meeting' 'Seeds' 'Conference' 'Dyalog' 'Alpha' 'Omega'
 lipsumвЖРgenerator.lipsum

вНЭ SETUP
 DвЖР#.DCMS

вНЭ GENERATE
 nвЖР100
 вОХRLвЖР42

вНЭ Use вОХDF to give each namespace a name that can be used to look up into SQL table metadata
 event_typeвЖР(
     type:(vocab:keywords вЛД max:1)generator.Name n
     description:(vocab:lipsum вЛД max:65535)generator.Text n
     url_slug:generator.URL n
 )
 event_type.вОХDF'event_type'

 eventвЖР()
 event.titleвЖР(vocab:thing_names вЛД max:2)generator.NameвН£{вИІ/вЙ†вНµ}n
 event.(start end)вЖРgenerator.DateTime¬®2вНіn
 event.typeвЖР?nвНіn
 event.url_slugвЖР'-'@(' 'вИШ=)¬®¬ѓ1 вОХC event.title
 event.вОХDF'event'
 example_eventвЖРвКГevent.url_slug   вНЭ Use example_event in DummyData.TestGETVideos_EventShortname

 organisationвЖР()
 organisation.nameвЖР(vocab:thing_names вЛД max:1)generator.Name n
 organisation.вОХDF'organisation'

 personвЖР()
 person.nameвЖР(vocab:person_names вЛД max:3)generator.Name n
 person.organisation_idвЖР?nвНіn
 person.вОХDF'person'

 presentation_typeвЖР(type:(вКВ?nвНівЙҐkeywords)вМЈkeywords)
 presentation_type.вОХDF'presentation_type'

 presentationвЖР()
 presentation.event_idвЖР?nвНіn-1   вНЭ events 1..n-1 only; event n guaranteed no presentations вЖТ has_videos=0
 presentation.event_id[1]вЖР1     вНЭ presentation 1 вЖТ event 1; combined with fixed_keys, event 1 has has_videos=1
 presentation.codeвЖР(vocab:вОХA,вОХD вЛД max:2 вЛД unique:1)generator.Name n
 presentation.titleвЖРstems
 presentation.title,вЖР(vocab:lipsum вЛД max:30)generator.Text n-вЙҐstems
 presentation.title[1],вЖРвКВ' dolor'   вНЭ Ensure a keyword is present in search results
 presentation.type_idвЖР?nвНіn
 presentation.descriptionвЖР(vocab:lipsum вЛД max:65535)generator.Text n
 presentation.presented_atвЖРgenerator.DateTime n
 presentation.вОХDF'presentation'

 presenterвЖР()
 вНЭ Using fixed keys in the presenter and presentation_media tables ensures that stems are found in video results for testing
 presenter.(presentation_id person_id)вЖРfixed_keysвЖР(1 2)(1 2)
 NotFixedKeysвЖР{~вИ®/,(вЖСfixed_keys)вНЈвН§1 2вКҐвНµ}
 presenter.(presentation_id person_id),вЖРвЖУвНЙ{?вНµвНівНЫвНіn}вН£{(NotFixedKeys вНЇ)вИІвИІ/вЙ†вНЇ}(n-вЙҐfixed_keys)2вНі0
 presenter.вОХDF'presenter'

 вНЭ Videos is not a table to insert, but its data is used in other tables and must be consistent, so we create it here and re-use it below
 videosвЖР()
 videos.titleвЖРstems
 videos.title,вЖР(vocab:lipsum вЛД max:30)generator.Text n-вЙҐstems
 videos.presentation_idвЖР?nвНіn
 videos.youtube_idвЖРвЖУ{(вОХA,вОХC вОХA)[?вНµвНівНЫвНі2√Ч26]}вН£{вИІ/вЙ†вНЇ}n 11вНі0
 example_videoвЖРвКГvideos.youtube_id   вНЭ Use example_video in DummyData.TestGETVideo

 presentation_mediaвЖР(type:nвНівКВ'youtube_video')
 presentation_media.(presentation_id media_id)вЖРfixed_keysвЖР(1 2)(1 2)
 presentation_media.(presentation_id media_id),вЖРвЖУвНЙ{?вНµвНівНЫвНіn n}вН£{(NotFixedKeys вНЇ)вИІвИІ/вЙ†вНЇ}(n-вЙҐfixed_keys)2вНі0   вНЭ Random unique pairs of numbers
 presentation_media.вОХDF'presentation_media'

 youtube_videoвЖР(
     youtube_id:videos.youtube_id
     title:videos.title
 )
 youtube_video.вОХDF'youtube_video'

вНЭ All generator functions take a right arg of number of records to generate
вНЭ Left argument is max size of data (length in bits), OR a special left argument for specific columns

 WrapBackticksвЖР(2вЖУвИК)'`'вИШ(', ',вК£,вК£,вН®вКҐ)¬®
 WrapColonsвЖР(1вЖУвИК)(',:',':',вН®вКҐ)¬®

 :For table :In event_type event organisation person presentation_type presentation presenter presentation_media youtube_video
     вОХвЖРnameвЖРвНХtable
     table.idвЖРвН≥n
     tidвЖРD.GLOBAL.tablesвН≥вКВname
     cidвЖР(columnвЖРtidвКГD.GLOBAL.columns)вН≥table.вОХNL ¬ѓ2
     typeвЖРcidвКВвНЫвМЈtidвКГD.GLOBAL.type_sqapl
     columnвЖРcidвКВвНЫвМЈcolumn
     col_specвЖРWrapBackticks column
     type_specвЖРWrapColons type
     sqlвЖР'INSERT INTO ',name,' (',col_spec,') VALUES (',type_spec,')'
     dataвЖРвНЙвЖСtable вОХVGET table.вОХNL ¬ѓ2
     D.SQL.Do'DELETE from ',name
     D.SQL.DoBulk sql data
 :EndFor




